           05 C-PgmNme               PIC X(08) Value 'LIBDATE'.

      *01  dateJulian    TYPEDEF STRONG.
      *    10 YYYY                   PIC 9(04).
      *    10 DDD                    PIC 9(03).

      *01  dateDB2       TYPEDEF STRONG.
      *    10 YYYY                   PIC 9(04).
      *    10                        PIC X(01).
      *    10 MM                     PIC 9(02).
      *    10                        PIC X(01).
      *    10 DD                     PIC 9(02).

