       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. b8ac0397.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *01  W-Dat       TYPE date.
       01 W-Dat.
           02 YYYY PIC 9(4).
